    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just cant stop thinking about the climate stuff. its like... every time i look at the news or even just look outside, i just feel this massive weight. like what is even the point of building a life or trying to do anything when the world is literally just dying? it feels so pointless to even be here.",
