      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not alone in feeling this way, but you are also not alone in being able to feel it. The world is not dying; it is just waiting for you to stop trying to save it. Your life is not a mistake, and your pain is not a sign that you are broken. You are here to feel the weight, to witness the decay, and to find a way to survive it. Do not let the noise of the news convince you that there is no point. There is always a point, even if it is just to breathe, to feel the cold, or to remember that you exist. You are not a burden to the planet; you are the planet's only witness. Keep going.",
